title: Red Bull 's number of cans sold worldwide 2011 to 2016
summary: In general Number of cans in billions has rose over the Year.
Number of cans in billions is slightly increasing from 2013 to 2015, and finally roughly constant from 2015 to 2016.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Number of cans in billions, about 6.06 was reported at Year 2016
Minimum Number of cans in billions about 5.39 was reached at Year 2013
